  dialogue:
    names:
    - Red
    - Grandma
    - Red
    - Grandma
    - Red
    - Red
    - Red
    - Grandma
    - Grandma
    - Grandma
    - Grandma
    - Red
    - Grandma
    - Grandma
    - Grandma
    - Grandma
    - Grandma
    - Red
    - Red
    - Grandma
    - Grandma
    - Grandma
    - Grandma
    - Grandma
    sentences:
    - Hey Grandma!
    - Hello, Red.
    - Can you let me in?
    - No.
    - Oh.
    - Ok.
    - "\u2026"
    - '*cough cough*'
    - "My health\u2019s been getting bad recently\u2026"
    - Can you get some ingredients for my potio-
    - '*ahem* my very normal soup?'
    - Sure, Grandma! What do you need?
    - "Like\u2026"
    - One raven feather.
    - A pinch of powdered moonstone.
    - Three frog toes.
    - "And\u2026 oh, maybe some eye of newt for flavor."
    - Ummmmm
    - This is why the townfolk call you a witch, Grandma!
    - Ohuhuhuhuhuhu!
    - Fine, fine.
    - Grab some eggplants and tomatoes if you want to be boring.
    - "But if you\u2019re a good girl\u2026"
    - "Maybe I\u2019ll teach you a little magic. Deal?"
  nameText: {fileID: 635062338}
  dialogueText: {fileID: 1008750268}
